\newlabel{fig:depression_heatmap}{{9}{11}{Heatmap of salinity depression ($\Delta S$, psu) for the top 50 most-affected sites across months. Peak depression at AK-PWS-002 reaches 15.0 psu in June. The symmetric melt pulse shape is visible in the temporal pattern}{figure.caption.11}{}}
